AICShortDescription.English:
stsw AIC inspired by Krarilotus aggressive AI v1.3 (should be played together with stsw AIV).

-General:
	-All AIs CriticalPopularity set to 6000
	-All AIs LowestPopularity set to 9000
	-All AIs HighestPopularity set to 9900
	-All AIs have customized TaxesMin (mostly 3)
	-All AIs have customized TaxesMax (mostly 11)
	-All AIs PopulationPerFarm set to 2
	-All AIs PopulationPerWoodcutter set to 1
	-All KIs PopulationPerQuarry have customized values (mostly 8)
	-All KIs PopulationPerIronmine have customized values (mostly 12)
	-All KIs PopulationPerPitchrig have customized values (mostly 20)
	-All AIs BuildInterval set to 2
	-All AIs ResourceRebuildDelay set to 4
	-All AIs MaxFood set to 40 (or 80 if they have DoubleRationsFoodThreshold > 0)
	-All AIs Minimum{food} set to 8
	-All AIs MinimumWheat set to 8 if AI produces bread
	-All AIs MinimumHop set to 4 if AI produces beer
	-All AIs TradeAmountFood set to 8
	-All AIs TradeAmountEquipment set to 4
	-All AIs AIRequestDelay set to 12
	-All AIs MinimumGoodsRequiredAfterTrade set to 0
	-All AIs DoubleRationsFoodThreshold set to 40 if they use double rations or 0 if they don't
	-All AIs MaxWood set to 72
	-All AIs MaxStone set to 72
	-All AIs MaxResourceOther set to 12
	-All AIs MaxBeer set to 8
	-All AIs MaxResourceVariance set to 0
	-All AIs DefSiegeEngineGoldThreshold set to 2000
	-All AIs DefSiegeEngineBuildDelay set to 4
	-All AIs DefWalls set to 87.5% of DefTotal
	-All AIs RaidUnitsRandom set to 25% of RaidUnitsBase
	-All AIs RaidRetargetDelay set to 4 (if only melee), 20 (if only ranged) or 12 (if both)
	-All AIs AttForceSupportAllyThreshold set to 0
	-All AIs AttForceRandom set to 20% of AttForceBase
	-All AIs CowThrowInterval set to 120
	-All AIs AttMaxEngineers set to all needed for SiegeEngines + 2
	-All AIs AttUnitBackup set to none
	-All AIs AttUnitSiegeDefGroupsCount set to 1
	-All AIs AttMainGroupsCount set to 2
	-All AIs TargetChoice set to Closest

-Unchanged from Krarilotus aggressive AI v1.3:
	-All AIs Unknown variables
	-All AIs MinimumGoodsRequiredAfterTrade set to 0
	-All AIs RecruitGoldThreshold
	-All AIs DefWallPatrolRallyTime and DefWallPatrolGroups
	-All AIs RecruitProb variables
	-All AIs RecruitInterval variables
	-All AIs AttForceSupportAllyThreshold set to 0
	-All AIs AttForceRallyPercentage, AttAssaultDelay, AttUnitPatrolRecommandDelay
